        h5 Pretty small, huh? <img src="/assets/images/magnify.png" class="emoji xsmall"> 

        h2 That was fun! Let's get to <a href="/work">work</a>! <img src="/assets/images/party.png" class="emoji large">
      
      include includes/footer
